    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Always Home</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Bob Meyer letter praises David LaChapelle's June 10 article on New Yorkers who keep to their apartments all the time</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>My thanks to David LaChapelle (June 10) for his touching and sensitive look into a few remarkable lives ''contained within four walls.'' The stories show how our memories, dreams and inner resources can sometimes stretch far beyond our physical space.</p>
        <p>The article was great food for the heart and soul.</p>
        <p>Bob Meyer  Scotia, N.Y.</p>
      </block>
